anyOf.description:
An empty permission you can use to modify the global scope.

## Example

```json
{
  "identifier": "read-documents",
  "windows": ["main"],
  "permissions": [
    "fs:allow-read",
    {
      "identifier": "fs:scope",
      "allow": [
        "$APPDATA/documents/**/*"
      ],
      "deny": [
        "$APPDATA/documents/secret.txt"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

